    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-octane roguelite ARPG (Diablo-like) fused with node alchemy — morph your dynamic node matrix, collect epic loot, and dominate the battlefield with unstoppable power.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cut to the Chase</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/7da1b040a2eb8a9dd1d90d3d7298e55a.poster.avif?t=1768201773\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/7da1b040a2eb8a9dd1d90d3d7298e55a.webm?t=1768201773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget bloated lore —dive straight into streamlined combat and progression that rewards smart builds.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Node Alchemy, Legendary Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/3825cd3819683a85945f2ff9ec6366d9.poster.avif?t=1768201773\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/3825cd3819683a85945f2ff9ec6366d9.webm?t=1768201773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast skill tree with over 1,300 nodes. Transmute entire node categories—turn defense into offense or swap one skill for another. Stack node multipliers to amplify your favorite abilities and achieve exponential growth. Master complex, multi-layered synergies as you sculpt your character into a living legend.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hordes and Swarm Lords</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/5afefe1f489acbf272f8138c03411c1b.poster.avif?t=1768201773\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/5afefe1f489acbf272f8138c03411c1b.webm?t=1768201773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight through relentless insect arenas—adapt your build to crush swarming hordes and towering boss monstrosities. Venture further and face ever-more formidable Swarm Lords—push your build beyond its limits.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sandbox of Destruction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/40dd8c5102c066148ed3f2a642b04d0b.poster.avif?t=1768201773\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061690/extras/40dd8c5102c066148ed3f2a642b04d0b.webm?t=1768201773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine tons of weapons for layered carnage that never gets old. Your build chooses how the swarm gets erased.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique art style and insect‑themed world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1,300+‑node skill tree</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Node transmutation and multiplication</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Node‑based meta‑progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally‑generated levels and items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless replayability</p></li></ul>",
